    "desc": "Meet the first 100% all natural Sichuan chili sauce, proudly crafted in Chengdu. Hot, spicy, crispy, numbing and deliciously savory. We bring you deep flavor to power your food.",
    "navbar": "Shop all\nShop Gifts\nOur Story\nRecipes\nLogin",
    "text": "THE HOLIDAY SALE: SAVE UP TO 30% OFF JING’S FAVES 🎁  SHOP SALE\nFREE SHIPPING OVER $50 📦\nGET A FREE SHORTY SPICE SET WHEN YOU SPEND $75+ ✨\nFly by Jing\nShop all\nShop Gifts\nOur Story\nRecipes\nLogin\nSAVE ON JING’S FAVES\nTake up to 30% off Jing’s top gift picks across gift sets, best-sellers, and more. Plus, score a free Shorty Spice Set ($25 value) on orders over $75.\nSHOP ALL\nSauces\nDumplings\nPantry\nSets\nMerch\nWelcome to\nthe flyest\nMade by Jing, but you can have some too.\nFREE SPOON\nHoliday\nTriple Threat\nnow 25% off\nShop Now\n-$45$33\nAdd to Cart\nBest Value\nTis The\nSeason(ing) Box\nnow 30% off\nShop Now\n-$140$98\nAdd to Cart\nIncludes Sauce\nSalsero\nServe Set\nnow 20% off\nShop Now\n-$120$96\nAdd to Cart\nBig\nSteamy\nnow 20% off\nShop Now\n-$100$80\nAdd to Cart\nThe\nBiggies\nnow 20% off\nShop Now\n-$64$51\nAdd to Cart\nBACK IN STOCK\nThe Hot\nPot Starter Set\nnow 20% off\nShop Now\n-$135$108\nAdd to Cart\nLucky 88\nSpice Lovers\nthe ultimate Sichuan pantry\nShop Now\n-$110$88\nAdd to Cart\nBest Seller\nSichuan\nChili Crisp\nsavory, hot, tingly\nShop Now\n-$15+\nAdd to Cart\n\"Your Home Cooking Needs Chili Crisp.\"\n\n\nFREE SPOON\nHoliday Triple Threat\nnow 25% off\n★★★★★ 3094 Reviews\nOur best-selling trio of addictive Sichuan sauces. Includes a limited-edition spoon for easy drizzling.\nWhats inside\nSichuan Chili Crisp\nThe first & only 100% all-natural Sichuan chili sauce, proudly crafted in Chengdu. Use it on everything. Yes, even that.\nZhong Sauce\nInspired by the popular, classic Chengdu street snack Zhong Dumplings, Zhong Sauce is sweet, tangy, spicy, and umami-rich all at once.\nMala Spice Mix\nMala, the signature flavor of Sichuan cuisine means \"spicy and numbing\". This dry spice blend adds oomph to any spice rub, batter, or rim of a marg on a Friday night.\nProduct information\nAdd to cart\n$45 $34\nYou will find yourself putting this on everything\nHow we compare\nFly by Jing\nOther Chili Oil\nOther Chili Sauce\nOther Hot Sauce\nSpice Level\nmedium\nmedium\nmedium\nmedium\nFlavor Profile\nsavory, deep, umami rich\nhot, crispy\nhot, acidic, sweet\nhot, acidic\nAll Natural\nSmall Batch Crafted\nSugar Free\nNo Artificial Preservatives\nNo MSG\nNON GMO\nMORE FIRE FLAVOR\nThe Dumpling\nDip Trio\nfor all your dipping needs\nShop Now\n-$50$45\nAdd to Cart\nCore\nFour\nheat four ways\nShop Now\n-$60$54\nAdd to Cart\n5 stars\nYes, this lives up to the hype.\n—@butteryexistence\n5 stars\nTHE G-O-A-T. I've used almost an entire jar in a week, that's how good this stuff is. If a dish doesn't turn out, I just throw some chili crisp on it and that problem is solved.\n—Christina S.\nelectrify your inbox ⚡️\n10% off your first order when you sign up for our mouthwatering emails. mmmmm.\nsign up\nShop\nAccount\nSubscriptions\nRewards\nOur Story\nRecipes\nContact\nFAQ\nWholesale\nStore Locator\nCorporate Gifting\nTerms of Service\nPrivacy Policy\nAccessibility\nSitemap\nFly By Jing\n© Fly By Jing 2022\nBranding & website by\nDay Job\nClose form 1",
